title: His Own Worst Enemy: The Rise and Fall of Jon Jones  | Part 1

media:group.media:title: His Own Worst Enemy: The Rise and Fall of Jon Jones  | Part 1
media:group.media:description:
In the first part of this series exploring the career of Jon Jones, we take a look at his early years in the UFC. We watch as he becomes the youngest champion in UFC history, then defeats a legendary lineup of opponents. But even at this early stage of his MMA career, there were feuds and controversies that would foreshadow future events.
